<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>To use Qt Network Authorization classes, add this directive into C++ files:</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="cpp">#include &lt;QtNetworkAuth&gt;
</db:programlisting>
<db:para>To link against the Qt Network Authorization module, add this line to the project file:</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="cpp">QT += network networkauth
</db:programlisting>
